data.description: A truly great home to make your own situated on almost a quarter acre lot, spacious yard space for all your activities and a carport for storage. The interior boasts new flooring through out, vaulted primary on the main floor with private half bath, and a roomy living and family room - great for hosting! Skylight in the open kitchen allows for a naturally bright space to cook and have an abundant amount of space to do so. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
